                            <comment id="14318207" author="githubbot" created="Thu, 12 Feb 2015 13:55:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user tillrohrmann opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/388&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/388&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1533&quot; title=&quot;NullPointerException in SlotSharingGroupAssignment.addSharedSlotAndAllocateSubSlot&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-1533&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-1533&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;runtime&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Fixes NPE in the scheduler&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Adds checks to the method ```Scheduler.getFreeSubSlotForTask``` to handle failed shared slot allocations. Before the slot was given to the ```SlotSharingGroupAssignment``` without checking that it is not null. Consequently, a NullPointerException could occur in the ```SlotSharingGroupAssignment```.&lt;/p&gt;

