&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1533&quot; title=&quot;NullPointerException in SlotSharingGroupAssignment.addSharedSlotAndAllocateSubSlot&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-1533&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-1533&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;runtime&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Fixes NPE in the scheduler where the allocated shared slots are not properly checked.&lt;/p&gt;

